headline: Should You Revisit DoorDash After Its 92% Run and New Alcohol Delivery Expansion?
summary: Thinking about what to do with DoorDash stock right now? You are not alone. Whether you have been following every earnings call or just noticed DASH's sharp moves lately, the stock is right in the spotlight for growth and risk watchers alike. Over the past year, DoorDash has powered higher by an incredible 92% and is up more than 44% since the start of this year. That kind of action tends to grab attention and spark questions: does that momentum mean the stock is getting ahead of itself, or...
